===Transitive verb===
{{rfc-trverb|Transitive verb}}
{{en-verb|inf=[[kick]] [[start]]}}

# To start a motorcycle
# To [[start]] or begin strongly or quickly.
#:''To kick-start your learning, let's summarize the basics.''

===Usage notes===
Noun senses 3 and 4, and verb sense 3, are considered incorrect in some circles; in all probability, the use of ''kick-start'' to mean "revitalize" or "provide impetus" was derived from the [[metaphor]]ical use of ''[[jump-start]]'' in that sense.

